				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "OBAUjI9fS2CA0g4WQNJ/4g=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The {{gtPackage:Gt4Cloudflare}} package includes a **webhook hosting service** built on Cloudflare Workers. It deploys a JavaScript Worker to Cloudflare's edge network that receives HTTP webhooks, optionally verifies HMAC-SHA256 signatures, and stores events in Workers KV for later retrieval from GT.\n\nThis is useful for receiving webhooks from services like Storylane, Salesforce, GitHub, etc. without running a local server — the Worker runs 24/7 on Cloudflare's global network."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:20.530903-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:20.530903-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "SIuhCXalTZ27dH5RdZg43g=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Setup\n\nYou need a Cloudflare account with Workers enabled (free tier is fine — 100k requests/day). Get your API token from the Cloudflare dashboard with **Workers Scripts** and **Workers KV Storage** permissions. Save it to `~/.secrets/cloudflare-api-key.txt`. You also need your **Account ID** (visible on the Workers dashboard)."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:24.205038-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:24.205038-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "n+uIULLFSYWJIYCigXWj9w=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Quick Start: Deploy a Webhook Worker"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:28.223999-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:28.223999-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "FZdKPBfYSd+auZcTCdfhgA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Create a {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWorkersClient}}, then use {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookWorker}} to deploy with a single message:"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:34.046866-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:34.046866-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "9IS/yZufSzC1SDxJ+Ak1aQ=="
				},
				"code" : "\"1. Create a Workers client\"\nclient := Gt4CloudflareWorkersClient withApiKeyFromFile\n\taccountId: 'YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID'.\n\n\"2. Create and deploy a webhook Worker\"\nwebhook := (Gt4CloudflareWebhookWorker\n\tclient: client\n\tscriptName: 'storylane-webhook'\n\tsecret: 'your-shared-secret')\n\tdeploy.\n\n\"3. Your webhook is now live!\"\nwebhook publicUrl.\n\"=> 'https://storylane-webhook.your-subdomain.workers.dev'\""
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:41.753672-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:41.753672-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "hCuJJSBPQcys8f79ViGkrA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The `deploy` method does three things automatically:\n1. Creates a **KV namespace** (e.g. `storylane-webhook-events`) to store incoming events\n2. Uploads the **webhook handler Worker** script with KV + secret bindings\n3. Enables the **workers.dev subdomain** so the Worker gets a public URL\n\nCopy the `publicUrl` and paste it into your webhook provider's configuration (e.g. Storylane settings)."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.335479-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.335479-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "kLrCrrH/TYybrY3y8k8WfQ=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Retrieving Events\n\nOnce webhooks are flowing, retrieve them from KV as rich {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookEvent}} objects:"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.365498-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.365498-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "hia7NvpzTdKrlOAt/w8IFQ=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Fetch all stored events (newest first in the GT inspector)\"\nevents := webhook fetchEvents.\n\n\"Inspect a single event\"\nevent := events items first.\nevent timestamp.    \"=> '2025-04-10T14:30:00.000Z'\"\nevent method.       \"=> 'POST'\"\nevent sourceIp.     \"=> '203.0.113.42'\"\nevent headers.      \"=> a Dictionary with all HTTP headers\"\nevent body.         \"=> the raw webhook payload string\"\nevent parsedBody.   \"=> parsed JSON dictionary (if body is JSON)\""
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.386608-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:20:53.386608-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "Ag0+xnJGQ6CwKjmi3A8gpw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Each event stores the full HTTP request: method, URL, path, all headers, the raw body, and the source IP (via Cloudflare's `cf-connecting-ip` header). Events are stored with a **30-day TTL** in KV automatically."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:03.827849-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:03.827849-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "YEViiSfbREKo7+aST+1jcA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Integration with Storylane\n\nTo use as a Storylane webhook endpoint:\n1. Deploy the webhook Worker with the same shared secret configured in Storylane\n2. Copy the `publicUrl` and paste it into **Storylane > Settings > Webhooks > URL**\n3. Set the shared secret in Storylane to match the `secret:` you passed during deploy\n4. The Worker automatically verifies `x-storylane-signature` headers using HMAC-SHA256\n\nThe events stored in KV contain the full Storylane payload in `body` — use `parsedBody` to access fields like lead email, company name, completion percentage, etc."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:03.860412-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:03.860412-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "2ldrGbSHRAOLsK5cs6TDpQ=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Example: Processing Storylane webhook events\"\nevents := webhook fetchEvents.\nevents items do: [ :event |\n\t| payload |\n\tpayload := event parsedBody.\n\tTranscript\n\t\tshow: (payload at: 'name' ifAbsent: [ 'unknown' ]);\n\t\tshow: ' — ';\n\t\tshow: ((payload at: 'lead' ifAbsent: [ nil ])\n\t\t\tifNil: [ 'anonymous' ]\n\t\t\tifNotNil: [ :lead | lead at: 'email' ifAbsent: [ '?' ] ]);\n\t\tcr ]"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
