					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:13.261751-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:13.261751-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "+60lC70USQGpMFYPUvw0+Q=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Signature Verification\n\nThe Worker supports HMAC-SHA256 signature verification for multiple webhook providers. When a `secret` is configured, the Worker checks these headers (in order):\n- `x-storylane-signature` (Storylane)\n- `x-hub-signature-256` (GitHub)\n- `x-webhook-signature` (generic)\n\nIf a secret is set and no valid signature header is present, the Worker returns **401 Unauthorized**. Without a secret, all POST requests are accepted (useful for development)."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:13.276069-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:21:13.276069-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "UB5na7kxTyGBftabAfG4OA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Managing the Worker\n\nThe {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookWorker}} provides actions in the GT inspector toolbar: **Deploy** (play button) and **Teardown** (cancel button). You can also manage programmatically:"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
