				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Worker HTTP Endpoints\n\nThe deployed webhook Worker exposes these endpoints:\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| POST | `/` | Receive a webhook event (stores in KV, verifies signature if secret set) |\n| GET | `/events` | List all stored events as JSON array (newest first, max 100) |\n| GET | `/events/{key}` | Retrieve a single event by its KV key |\n| GET | `/health` | Health check returning `{ \"status\": \"ok\" }` |"
			},
