					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Architecture\n\nThe webhook service is built from these classes:\n\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWorkersClient}} — REST client for the Cloudflare Workers API (scripts, KV, subdomain)\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookWorker}} — High-level manager that deploys a webhook-receiving Worker + KV store\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWorkerScript}} / {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWorkerScripts}} — Worker script metadata models\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareKvNamespace}} / {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareKvNamespaces}} — KV namespace models with key operations\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareKvEntry}} — Single KV key/value entry\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookEvent}} / {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWebhookEvents}} — Webhook event models parsed from KV\n- {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareWorkersExamples}} — Fixture-based offline examples"
			}
		]
